%3ERental%20owners%20say%20their%20property%20values%20will%20tank.%20One%20said%20his%20family%20may%20have%20to%20leave%20Maui.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20say%20the%20ban%20would%20increase%20the%20long-term%20housing%20supply%20and%20likely%20reduce%20housing%20prices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Church%20has%20lived%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhawaiian-local-thoughts-feelings-about-tourism-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMaui%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20than%20two%20decades%2C%20while%20his%20long-term%20partner%20and%20fianc%C3%A9e%2C%20with%20whom%20he%20has%20a%20daughter%2C%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20and%20saving%20for%20years%2C%20Church%20started%20purchasing%20properties%20to%20operate%20as%20rentals%20in%20September%202022%20and%20now%20has%20four%20units.%20His%20vacation%20rentals%20are%20now%20the%20primary%20source%20of%20income%20for%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaui%20officials%20have%20rolled%20out%20a%20plan%20to%20phase%20out%207%2C000-plus%20short-term%20rentals%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20open%20up%20more%20housing%20for%20local%20residents%20and%20bring%20down%20housing%20costs%20%E2%80%94%20a%20move%20that%20Church%20said%20will%20devastate%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20family%20is%20losing%20sleep%20every%20night%20over%20this%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Church%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20He%20said%20if%20the%20ban%20takes%20effect%2C%20he%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20pay%20his%20mortgage%20and%20would%20probably%20have%20to%20sell%20everything%20and%20leave%20Maui%2C%20where%20his%20fianc%C3%A9's%20family%20roots%20go%20back%20over%20a%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20enforcing%20this%20ban%2C%20they%20are%20going%20to%20bankrupt%20my%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20some%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20real%20estate%20in%20the%20US%2C%20Maui%20has%20long%20had%20housing%20issues.%20Hawaii's%20median%20home%20price%20is%20higher%20than%20nearly%20every%20other%20US%20state.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMaui%20specifically%20had%20a%20median%20home%20price%20of%20around%20%241.1%20million%20in%20July%202024%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20countrywide%20median%20home%20price%20of%20%24438%2C706%2C%20according%20to%20Redfin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20island's%20housing%20problems%20were%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaui-fires-where-to-visit-avoid-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildfire%20that%20devastated%20Lahaina%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20August%202023%2C%20destroying%20much%20of%20the%20downtown%20and%20displacing%20thousands%20of%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20to%20phase%20out%20some%20short-term%20rentals%20came%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20fire%2C%20but%20as%20a%20tourist%20destination%20with%20local%20housing%20issues%2C%20Maui%20is%20hardly%20alone.%20Barcelona%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbnb-numbers-shrink-hotel-prices-soar-ban-nyc-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20City%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20among%20the%20cities%20that%20have%20banned%20or%20implemented%20restrictions%20on%20Airbnb%20and%20vacation%20rentals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20an%20island%20the%20size%20of%20Maui%2C%20where%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffour-seasons-maui-manager-great-time-visit-deals-less-crowds-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etourism%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20responsible%20for%2070%25%20of%20every%20dollar%20generated%2C%20the%20consequences%20could%20be%20significant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22577b47e3-5221-4d7e-a6cd-34798463da7c%5C%22%3EOwners%20say%20their%20property%20values%20will%20tank%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%2C%20which%20applies%20to%20properties%20on%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3BMinatoya%20List%2C%26quot%3B%20includes%207%2C160%20units%20largely%20concentrated%20in%20the%20touristy%20areas%20of%20South%20Maui%2C%20primarily%20Kihei%2C%20and%20West%20Maui%2C%20mostly%20Kaanapali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20properties%20are%20technically%20zoned%20for%20residential%20apartments%20but%2C%20since%202001%2C%20have%20been%20allowed%20to%20legally%20operate%20as%20short-term%20rentals%20%E2%80%94%20and%20have%20been%20taxed%20to%20that%20effect.%20The%20list%20is%20named%20for%20the%20city%20employee%20who%20initially%20wrote%20a%20memo%20about%20allowing%20the%20short-term%20rentals%2C%20which%20was%20eventually%20put%20into%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20view%20of%20fire%20damage%20in%20Lahaina%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d11a4b392a3bda9f236bb3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22723%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMuch%20of%20Maui's%20historic%20Lahaina%20town%20burned%20in%20the%20fire%20last%20year.%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMaui%20Mayor%20Richard%20Bissen%20earlier%20this%20year%20announced%20a%20plan%20to%20end%20those%20permissions.%20The%20Maui%20Planning%20Commission%20voted%20unanimously%20in%20favor%20of%20it%2C%20recommending%20it%20be%20approved%20by%20the%20city%20council.%20If%20approved%2C%20the%20ban%20will%20take%20effect%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20area%2C%20in%202025%20and%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChurch%20said%20three%20of%20his%20four%20properties%20are%20on%20the%20list%2C%20but%20when%20he%20bought%20them%20in%202022%20and%202023%2C%20he%20had%20no%20idea%20the%20list%20existed.%20When%20researching%20the%20properties%2C%20he%20confirmed%20their%20tax%20status%20as%20short-term%20rentals%20on%20the%20county%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20units%20were%20marketed%20and%20sold%20to%20him%20as%20vacation%20rentals%20and%20that%20no%20one%2C%20not%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20or%20a%20government%20official%2C%20mentioned%20the%20list%20to%20him.%20Church%20said%20other%20owners%20he%20knows%20said%20the%20same%20thing%20and%20are%20also%20concerned%20about%20the%20financial%20impacts%20of%20the%20ban.%20The%20Maui%20County%20mayor's%20office%20did%20not%20provide%20comment%20when%20reached%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJason%20Gobey%2C%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbnb-hosts-competition-summer-travel-direct-bookings-influencers-boost-revenue-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshort-term%20rental%20owner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20BI%20he%20researched%20and%20spoke%20to%20real-estate%20agents%20as%20well%20as%20others%20before%20buying%20his%20one-bedroom%20condo%20in%20Kihei%20in%202019.%20He%20also%20said%20he%20confirmed%20the%20property's%20tax%20status%20as%20a%20short-term%20rental%20and%20had%20no%20idea%20there%20could%20be%20an%20issue%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGobey%20and%20his%20wife%20live%20in%20Arizona%20but%20spend%20about%20four%20months%20of%20the%20year%20on%20Maui.%20He%20said%20he%20does%20not%20make%20a%20substantial%20profit%20on%20his%20condo%20but%20that%20buying%20it%20and%20renting%20it%20out%20was%20the%20only%20way%20they%20could%20afford%20to%20visit%20Maui%20as%20often%20as%20they%20do%2C%20during%20which%20time%20they%20are%20also%20spending%20heavily%20on%20the%20local%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20bought%20it%20to%20use%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20need%20some%20income%20off%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20owners%20said%20their%20property%20value%20is%20going%20to%20plunge%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20ban.%20They%20said%20plenty%20of%20similar%20units%20have%20been%20listed%20for%20sale%20since%20the%20ban%20was%20proposed%2C%20but%20that%20no%20one%20is%20buying%20them.%20They%20feel%20certain%20that%20if%20they%20eventually%20sell%20their%20properties%20it%20will%20be%20at%20a%20substantial%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20some%20of%20the%20Minatoya%20List%20properties%20will%20likely%20be%20converted%20to%20long-term%20rentals%2C%20Church%20said%20it%20is%20not%20financially%20feasible%20for%20him.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDue%20to%20the%20high%20costs%20associated%20with%20property%20maintenance%2C%20he%20thinks%20he%20would%20have%20to%20charge%20far%20too%20much%20to%20make%20a%20long-term%20rental%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGobey%20said%20since%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20spend%20a%20month%20on%20Maui%20every%20few%20months%20or%20so%2C%20his%20unit%20will%20just%20sit%20empty%20when%20they%20are%20not%20on%20the%20island.%20Both%20owners%20said%20the%20people%20who%20help%20them%20maintain%20the%20units%2C%20like%20proper%20managers%20and%20cleaners%2C%20would%20also%20lose%20work%20as%20a%20direct%20result%20of%20the%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Beach%20scene%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d11ac1392a3bda9f236bbe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMany%20of%20the%20properties%20on%20the%20Minatoya%20List%20are%20located%20in%20Kihei%2C%20a%20popular%20area%20for%20tourists.%3Cp%3ESmith%20Collection%2FGado%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228211afe0-0b5d-4768-8694-bf33b931d67c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20ban%20should%20help%20Maui's%20housing%20problem%2C%20but%20the%20wider%20impacts%20are%20unclear%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20owners%20also%20said%20they%20did%20not%20think%20phasing%20out%20their%20rentals%20would%20actually%20solve%20Maui's%20housing%20crisis%2C%20saying%20the%20value%20of%20the%20properties%20would%20likely%20still%20be%20higher%20than%20the%20average%20family%20could%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Justin%20Tyndall%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20of%20economics%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Hawaii%20at%20Manoa%2C%20said%20the%20policy%20change%20would%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fuhero.hawaii.edu%2Fmaui-short-term-rentals-the-minatoya-list-and-housing-supply%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esignificant%20positive%20impact%20on%20housing%20in%20Maui%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20increasing%20the%20long-term%20residential%20housing%20stock%20by%2013%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20would%20just%20be%20a%20huge%20flood%20of%20new%20units.%20Some%20of%20them%20would%20end%20up%20for%20sale%2C%20or%20some%20of%20them%20would%20be%20rented%20out%20to%20locals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20definitely%20make%20housing%20more%20affordable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20many%20of%20the%20properties%20would%20still%20be%20unattainable%20to%20lower-income%20residents%2C%20increasing%20the%20supply%20of%20housing%20would%20likely%20put%20downward%20pressure%20on%20home%20prices%20and%20rents%20more%20broadly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETyndall%20said%20Maui's%20housing%20issue%20largely%20comes%20down%20to%20a%20lack%20of%20housing%20supply%20resulting%20in%20extremely%20high%20prices.%20A%20significant%20driver%20of%20that%20is%20how%20few%20new%20construction%20projects%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethere%20have%20been%20on%20the%20island%20over%20the%20past%20two%20decades%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20government%20regulations%20that%20make%20obtaining%20a%20permit%20difficult%20and%20costly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20some%20of%20those%20regulations%20make%20sense%2C%20like%20those%20intended%20to%20protect%20ecologically%20sensitive%20areas%2C%20while%20others%20are%20misguided%2C%20and%20that%20there%20are%20changes%20the%20government%20could%20make%20to%20encourage%20developers%20to%20build%20more%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20benefit%20of%20adding%20the%20Minatoya%20List%20properties%20to%20the%20housing%20stock%20is%20that%20they%20are%20already%20built.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20property%20value%20of%20those%20units%20will%20almost%20certainly%20go%20down%2C%20but%20that%20that's%20not%20a%20bad%20thing%20for%20the%20broader%20Maui%20housing%20problem.%20He%20also%20noted%20that%2085%25%20of%20the%20units%20on%20the%20list%20are%20owned%20by%20people%20who%20live%20out%20of%20state%2C%20while%2092%25%20are%20owned%20by%20people%20who%20don't%20live%20on%20Maui.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20said%20there's%20a%20consensus%20among%20experts%20that%20the%20change%20will%20benefit%20Maui%20housing%20by%20increasing%20supply%20and%20bringing%20down%20costs%2C%20he%20is%20still%20looking%20into%20what%20the%20broader%20impacts%20might%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaui%20is%20so%20dependent%20on%20tourism%2C%20taking%20away%207%2C000%20visitor%20accommodation%20units%20will%20certainly%20reduce%20tourism%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20Tyndall%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20unclear%20by%20how%20much.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20most%20hotels%20on%20the%20island%20generally%20operate%20at%2060%20to%2070%25%20capacity%2C%20so%20some%20would-be%20short-term%20renters%20will%20likely%20end%20up%20there%2C%20but%20at%20this%20point%2C%20it's%20still%20a%20big%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20change%20leads%20to%20a%20significant%20reduction%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaui-food-truck-owner-irresponsible-to-tell-tourists-island-is-closed-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etourists%20visiting%20Maui%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20would%20mean%20less%20tax%20revenue%20for%20the%20county%20and%20job%20losses%20for%20people%20in%20the%20service%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20short-term%20rental%20owners%2C%20Tyndall%20said%20folks%20should've%20known%20this%20was%20a%20possibility%20and%20that%20many%20people%20who%20work%20in%20real%20estate%20at%20least%20knew%20about%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProperty%20investment%20involves%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20guarantee%20you%20can%20operate%20a%20va