C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20asked%20former%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20to%20take%20care%20not%20to%20create%20any%20row%20with%20comments%20at%20wrestlers%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20BJP%20MP%20faced%20allegations%20of%20sex%20harassment%20from%20some%20of%20the%20top%20athletes%20in%20the%20country%20including%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Sakshi%20Malik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20has%20alleged%20the%20allegations%20against%20him%20were%20a%20conspiracy%20hatched%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%20pointing%20at%20Ms%20Phogat%20and%20wrestler%20Bajrang%20Punia%20joining%20the%20Congress%20party%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20election%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(Mr%20Punia%20and%20Ms%20Phogat)%20were%20the%20faces...%20they%20were%20mohrey%20(pawns).%20They%20were%20used%20like%20pawns%20by%20(former%20Haryana%20Chief%20Minister)%20Bhupinder%20Hooda%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Congress%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20all%20conspired%20to%20gain%20a%20hold%20on%20the%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20and%20to%20attack%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20ideology...%20This%20team%20of%20Rahul%20(Gandhi)%2C%20the%20Congress%20keeps%20doing%20these%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%202012%20when%20Mr%20Singh%20first%20got%20control%20of%20the%20WFI%20after%20a%20bitter%20turf%20war%20with%20Mr%20Hooda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Mr%20Singh's%20latest%20comments%2C%20the%20BJP%20asked%20him%20not%20to%20pass%20any%20more%20comments%20against%20the%20wrestlers%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20sends%20a%20large%20number%20of%20sportspersons%20to%20national%20teams.%20Athletes%20in%20the%20state%20are%20seen%20to%20command%20large%20loyal%20followers%2C%20and%20this%20may%20have%20prompted%20the%20BJP%20to%20caution%20its%20former%20MP%20to%20keep%20quiet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20does%20not%20want%20to%20see%20any%20new%20narrative%20linked%20to%20the%20wrestlers'%20protest%2C%20which%20had%20drawn%20a%20lot%20of%20support%20in%20Haryana%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20the%20women%20wrestlers%2C%20the%20BJP%20did%20not%20give%20Mr%20Singh%20a%20ticket%20from%20Kaiserganj%20and%20made%20his%20son%20Karan%20Bhushan%20Singh%20the%20candidate%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaran%20Bhushan%20Singh%20won%20the%20election%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20over%201.48%20lakh%20votes%2C%20defeating%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20Bhagat%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20both%20Ms%20Phogat%20and%20Mr%20Punia%20said%20they%20would%20continue%20the%20fight%20against%20Mr%20Singh%20with%20the%20former%20asserting%20she%20would%20ensure%20that%20no%20woman%20faces%20what%20she%20had%20to%20go%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2030-year-old%2C%20who%20is%20a%20two-time%20world%20championships%20medallist%20besides%20being%20an%20Asiad%20gold-winner%2C%20will%20contest%20from%20Julana%20constituency.%20Mr%20Punia%20has%20been%20made%20the%20working%20chairman%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Kisan%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725796020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ffl8er4oo_brij-bhushan-sharan-singh_625x300_13_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjps-gag-order-on-brij-bhushan-as-wrestlers-join-congress-ahead-of-haryana-polls-sources-6518618%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20has%20asked%20former%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20(WFI)%20chief%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20to%20take%20care%20not%20to%20create%20any%20row%20with%20comments%20at%20wrestlers%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taiwan%20Teacher%20Earns%20Rs%202%20Crore%20A%20Year%20By%20Giving%20Math%20Lessons%20On%20Pornhub%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMeet%20Chang%20Hsu%2C%20the%20Taiwanese%20math%20teacher%20who%20has%20revolutionised%20online%20education%20with%20an%20unorthodox%20approach.%20In%20a%20bold%20move%20to%20make%20himself%20stand%20out%20in%20the%20crowded%20online%20tutoring%20space%2C%20Mr%20Hsu%C2%A0started%20uploading%20videos%20of%20math%20lessons%20on%20PornHub%2C%20a%20platform%20synonymous%20with%20adult%20content.%C2%A0With%20nearly%203%20million%20views%20and%20over%2013%2C000%20subscribers%2C%20his%20clickbait%20strategy%20paid%20off%2C%20driving%20traffic%20to%20his%20paid%20courses%20and%20boosting%20his%20income%20to%20a%20staggering%20%24270%2C000%20(Rs%C2%A02%2C26%2C76%2C719)%20per%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2C%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2021%2F11%2F03%2Ftaiwanese-math-teacher-uses-pornhub-to-reach-more-students%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3EMr%20Hsu%20is%20a%20seasoned%20mathematics%20educator%20with%20a%20Master's%20degree%20and%2015%20years%20of%20teaching%20experience.%20He%20initially%20uploaded%20his%20math%20lessons%20on%20YouTube%20but%20decided%20to%20diversify%20his%20platforms.%20In%20May%202020%2C%20he%20started%20uploading%20his%20calculus%20lessons%20to%20Pornhub%20as%20part%20of%20an%20innovative%20marketing%20strategy%20to%20showcase%20his%20teaching%20in%20unexpected%20places.%C2%A0His%20unorthodox%20approach%20proved%20effective%2C%20as%20many%20students%20who%20discovered%20his%20free%20lessons%20on%20Pornhub%20went%20on%20to%20enrol%20in%20his%20paid%20courses%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Hsu%2C%20who%20operates%20under%20the%20handle%20changshumath666%2C%20has%20a%20verified%20account%20on%20Pornhub.%20Under%20his%20channel%20slogan%20%26quot%3BPlay%20Hard%2C%20Study%20Hard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20creatively%20repurposes%20the%20adult%20website%20to%20make%20complex%20calculus%20concepts%20accessible%20to%20a%20wider%20audience.%C2%A0Interestingly%2C%20his%20Pornhub%20channel%20has%20now%20become%20a%20go-to%20destination%20for%20many%20students%20seeking%20to%20grasp%20the%20fundamentals%20of%20calculus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20unconventional%20approach%2C%20the%20teacher%20previously%20told%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%2C%20noindex%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmelmagazine.com%2Fen-us%2Fstory%2Fmath-lessons-on-pornhub%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMel%20Magazine%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20''Since%20very%20few%20people%20teach%20math%20on%20adult%20video%20platforms%2C%20and%20since%20there%20are%20so%20many%20people%20who%20watch%20videos%20on%20them%2C%20I%20thought%20that%20if%20I%20uploaded%20my%20videos%20there%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20would%20see%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20each%20video%2C%20the%20teacher%20appears%20in%20his%20signature%20grey%20hoodie%20and%20glasses%2C%20exuding%20quiet%20confidence%20as%20he%20tackles%20complex%20mathematical%20problems%20on%20a%20green%20board.%C2%A0His%20videos%20tend%20to%20last%20around%2040%20minutes%20and%20net%20around%2020%2C000%20viewers%20per%20clip%20on%20average.%C2%A0%20However%2C%20the%20teacher%20estimates%20that%20over%2060%25%20of%20his%20audience%20tunes%20in%20for%20entertainment%20value%20rather%20than%20a%20genuine%20interest%20in%20learning%20complex%20mathematical%20concepts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''People%20may%20not%20be%20interested%20in%20my%20videos%2C%20but%20they'll%20all%20know%20there's%20a%20teacher%20who%20teaches%20calculus%20on%20an%20adult%20video%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20admitted%20that%20he%20tried%20to%20further%20broaden%20his%20reach%20by%20uploading%20his%20math%20lessons%20to%20other%20adult%20websites.%20However%2C%20his%20efforts%20were%20met%20with%20resistance.%20Accor