der.com%2Fcategory%2Ffor-love-and-money%5C%22%3EFor%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20column%20from%20Business%20Insider%20answering%20your%20relationship%20and%20money%20questions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThis%20week%2C%20a%20reader%20is%20worried%20their%20daughters%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20the%20colleges%20they%20want.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOur%20columnist%20says%20that%20Ivy%20Leagues%20can%20be%20surprisingly%20affordable%2C%20and%20they%20can%20start%20saving%20now.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGot%20a%20question%20for%20our%20columnist%3F%20Write%20to%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDear%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20been%20encouraging%20my%20twin%20daughters%20to%20aim%20for%20the%20Ivy%20League%20their%20whole%20lives.%20As%20someone%20who%20took%20out%20student%20loans%20that%20I'm%20still%20paying%20off%2C%20I%20never%20worried%20about%20how%20they%20would%20pay%20for%20it.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20daughters%20are%20in%20high%20school%20now%2C%20though%2C%20and%20working%20so%20hard%20to%20make%20this%20dream%20come%20true%2C%20I'm%20starting%20to%20worry%20that%20it%20might.%20We%20are%20middle%20class%20at%20best.%20There%20is%20no%20way%20I%20can%20afford%20for%20my%20girls%20to%20go%20to%20Harvard%20or%20Yale%2C%20but%20I%20also%20hate%20to%20dissuade%20them%20from%20such%20an%20exciting%20goal%20over%20money.%20I%20also%20hate%20to%20burden%20their%20futures%20with%20student%20loans%20like%20I%20did.%20What%20should%20we%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBroke%20Parent%20of%20College%20Bound%20Twins%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDear%20Broke%20Parent%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20wager%20that%20most%20adults%20have%20yet%20to%20reconcile%20their%20dreams%20with%20reality.%20Few%20know%20if%20they%20have%20the%20skills%2C%20grit%2C%20or%20luck%20to%20see%20their%20big%20plans%20through%3B%20even%20when%20money%20is%20tight%2C%20the%20dream%20gets%20boring%2C%20and%20better%20offers%20come%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20I%20am%20a%2035-year-old%20woman%20still%20chasing%20a%2026-year-old%20dream%20of%20being%20a%20novelist%2C%20even%20though%20I%20have%20never%20made%20any%20money%20or%20progress%20in%20this%20endeavor.%20Meanwhile%2C%20my%20husband%20works%20in%20banking%2C%20makes%20a%20solid%20income%20for%20our%20family%2C%20and%20spends%20most%20of%20his%20time%20fantasizing%20about%20an%20alternate%20universe%20where%20he's%20crunching%20sports%20stats%20and%20interviewing%20basketball%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20adults%20I%20know%20are%20like%20either%20my%20husband%20or%20me%20%E2%80%94%20following%20their%20dreams%20well%20past%20the%20point%20of%20common%20sense%20or%20giving%20up%20on%20them%20before%20they%20even%20got%20started.%20Then%2C%20these%20same%20adults%20have%20kids%20who%20get%20told%20to%20believe%20in%20their%20dreams%2C%20and%20they'll%20come%20true.%20And%20so%20our%20kids%20tell%20us%20they%20want%20to%20be%20famous%20baseball%20players%2C%20ballerinas%2C%20and%20marine%20biologists%20in%20Central%20Kansas%2C%20and%20we%20know%20how%20to%20handle%20their%20dreams%20as%20well%20as%20we%20did%20our%20own.%20That%20is%20to%20say%2C%20not%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFostering%20those%20dreams%20can%20feel%20as%20dangerous%20as%20crushing%20them.%20But%20dreams%20are%20always%20good%2C%20even%20when%20they're%20not%20achievable%2C%20because%20they%20give%20us%20something%20to%20strive%20for.%20The%20dream%20you%20have%20instilled%20in%20your%20daughters%20is%20valuable%20for%20that%20reason%20alone.%20Don't%20beat%20yourself%20up%20over%20nourishing%20hopes%20that%20may%20not%20come%20true.%20Getting%20into%20the%20Ivy%20League%20is%20an%20ambitious%20goal%20for%20everyone.%20If%20your%20daughters%20can%20manage%20it%2C%20the%20last%20thing%20you%20should%20do%20is%20consider%20it%20a%20parenting%20fail%20because%20you%20can't%20put%20your%20money%20where%20your%20mouth%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20good%20news%20is%20that%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20a%20billionaire%20(or%20saddle%20your%20daughters%20with%20a%20lifetime%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstudent-loans%2Fbest-private-student-loans%5C%22%3Estudent%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E)%20to%20afford%20the%20Ivys%2C%20even%20with%20twins.%20To%20help%20me%20respond%20to%20your%20letter%2C%20I%20talked%20to%20a%20college%20admissions%20and%20tuition%20expert.%20Jeffrey%20Selingo%20is%20the%20best-selling%20author%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EWho%20Gets%20In%20%26amp%3B%20Why%3A%20A%20Year%20Inside%20College%20Admissions%3C%2Fspan%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelingo%20assured%20me%20that%20while%20Ivy%20League%20schools%20are%20expensive%2C%20their%20tuition%20is%20on%20par%20with%20those%20of%20other%20private%20universities.%20The%20main%20difference%20is%20that%20prestigious%20schools%20have%20more%20resources%20and%20are%20free%20to%20prioritize%20diversity.%20This%20diversity%20includes%20income%20and%20geography.%20To%20help%20kids%20living%20halfway%20across%20the%20country%20who%20can%20barely%20afford%20to%20travel%20to%20the%20college%20of%20their%20choice%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20tuition%2C%20most%20Ivy%20and%20Ivy%20League%20Plus%20schools%20cover%20all%20or%20at%20least%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20their%20students'%20%26quot%3Bdemonstrated%20need.%26quot%3B%20Demonstrated%20need%20is%20the%20gap%20between%20what%20you%20can%20afford%20and%20your%20daughters'%20achievement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20daughters%20must%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstudent-loans%2Fwhen-to-file-fafsa%5C%22%3Efile%20FAFSAs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20possibly%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstudent-loans%2Fcss-profile-deadline%5C%22%3ECSS%20profile%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20qualify%20for%20full%20demonstrated%20need.%20These%20formulas%20calculate%20how%20much%20aid%20your%20daughters%20will%20need%20based%20on%20your%20expected%20family%20contribution%20(how%20much%20they%20think%20you%20can%20afford)%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20attendance%20at%20their%20school%20of%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESelingo%20said%20that%20with%20your%20stated%20financial%20circumstances%20being%20%26quot%3Bmiddle%20class%20at%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20your%20daughters%20probably%20won't%20need%20to%20worry%20about%20paying%20much.%20But%20if%20they%20find%20that%20student%20loans%20will%20be%20a%20necessary%20part%20of%20their%20journey%2C%20he%20suggests%20you%20see%20them%20as%20investments%20rather%20than%20burdens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELook%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20loan%20versus%20your%20daughters'%20expected%20income.%20If%20they%20can%20reasonably%20plan%20to%20pay%20off%20their%20loans%20in%2010%20years%2C%20consider%20what%20they%20are%20paying%20for%20%E2%80%94%20learning%20from%20some%20of%20the%20best%20minds%20in%20the%20world%2C%20making%20priceless%20connections%2C%20and%20getting%20to%20put%20%26quot%3BYale%26quot%3B%20on%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20their%20lives.%20That%20said%2C%20you%20can%20always%20look%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstudent-loans%2Fwhat-is-pell-grant%5C%22%3EPell%20Grants%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20work-study%20opportunities%2C%20and%20private%20scholarships%20before%20you%20take%20on%20any%20loans.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fastweb.com%2Fppc%3Futm_source%3Dgoogle%26utm_medium%3Dppc%26ESRC%3Dfw_ggl.kw%26gad_source%3D1%26mkw%3