-room-that-cause-stress-according-to-therapists-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estraighten%20up%20the%20living%20room%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20mask%20the%20disorder%20that%20permeated%20our%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20house%20with%20two%20small%20kids%2C%20clutter%20was%20a%20given.%20But%20the%20mess%20in%20my%20family's%20home%20went%20beyond%20the%20usual%20toys%20on%20the%20floor%20or%20an%20overflowing%20hamper%20in%20the%20bathroom.%20Our%20house%20wasn't%20dirty%2C%20but%20it%20was%20full%20of%20things%20we%20didn't%20need%20%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstylist-updated-clothing-wardrobe-body-positivity-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eclothes%20that%20no%20longer%20fit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20threadbare%20towels%2C%20unused%20kitchen%20utensils%2C%20toys%20we'd%20outgrown.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f5bdbb34-3b5c-4e04-9b80-f4611ff9b48e%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20reason%20behind%20the%20clutter%20in%20my%20childhood%20home%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20most%20homes%2C%20I%20imagine%20these%20things%20would've%20been%20thrown%20away%20or%20perhaps%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-smaller-house-decluttering-tips-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebagged%20up%20and%20donated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20But%20not%20in%20our%20house.%20They%20filled%20cabinets%2C%20spilled%20from%20overstuffed%20drawers%2C%20and%20accumulated%20on%20surfaces%2C%20such%20as%20the%20dining%20room%20table%20or%20the%20kitchen%20counter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20my%20parents%20weren't%20hoarders%2C%20exactly.%20They%20were%20simply%20among%20a%20generation%20of%20Americans%20raised%20by%20parents%20who%20survived%20the%20Great%20Depression.%20On%20my%20father's%20side%