%3Cp%3EVice%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fharris-trump-race-to-the-middle-labor-day-election-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKamala%20Harris%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20are%20set%20to%20face%20off%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20a%20major%20moment%20that%20could%20swing%20an%20extraordinarily%20close%202024%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20be%20the%20first%20time%20Harris%20and%20Trump%20have%20ever%20met%20each%20other%20in%20person%2C%20a%20reminder%20of%20just%20how%20dramatically%20the%20contest%20changed%20after%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20dropped%20out%20of%20the%20race%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarris%20enters%20the%20debate%20will%20clear%20momentum.%20Trump%20has%20struggled%20to%20settle%20on%20a%20clear%20attack%20against%20her%20and%20has%20lost%20ground%20since%20Biden's%20exit.%20Still%2C%20national%20polling%20averages%20show%20Harris%20has%20only%20a%20slight%20lead.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20race%20is%20even%20closer%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbattleground-states-2024-presidential-election-road-white-house-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmall%20number%20of%20swing%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20will%20decide%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Friday%3Cu%3E%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%20only%20one%20state%2C%20Wisconsin%2C%20where%20Harris%20leads%2C%20has%20a%20larger%20than%203%20percentage%20point%20difference%20between%20the%20pair%20in%20The%20Washington%20Post's%20polling%20average.%20Election%20forecaster%20Nate%20Silver%20has%20Trump%20as%20the%20slight%20favorite%20to%20win%20the%20Electoral%20College%20and%20thus%20the%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20hemmed%20and%20hawed%20over%20the%20debate%20rules%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Biden's%20exit%2C%20but%20given%20Harris'%20momentum%2C%20he%20could%20never%20afford%20to%20seriously%20miss%20the%20face%20off.%20Just%20days%20before%20the%20debate%2C%20Harris%20agreed%20to%20mute%20the%20microphone%20of%20the%20candidate%20who%20is%20not%20speaking.%20Biden's%20team%20initially%20sought%20that%20rule%20change%20ahead%20of%20the%20June%20debate%2C%20but%20Harris'%20team%20had%20tried%20to%20push%20Trump%20into%20reverting%20back%20to%20a%20more%20free%20for%20fall%20format.%20Trump%20himself%20suggested%20he%20would%20be%20open%20to%20so-called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkamala-harris-donald-trump-debate-microphone-philadelphia-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bhot%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bopen%26quot%3B%20mics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20ultimately%20stuck%20by%20the%20terms%20that%20he%20and%20Biden%20agreed%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20vital%20facts%20you%20need%20to%20know%20before%20Tuesday%20night's%20debate.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22afefdb82-0d52-488d-b3ff-923ef909ac13%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20is%20it%20and%20how%20can%20I%20watch%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20debate%20between%20Harris%20and%20Trump%20is%20set%20for%20Tuesday%20at%209%20p.m.%20ET.%20ABC%20News%20will%20host%20the%20debate%2C%20but%20other%20major%20networks%20will%20offer%20a%20simulcast.%20The%20debate%20will%20stream%20on%20ABC%20News%20Live%2C%20Disney%2B%2C%20and%20Hulu.%20You%20don't%20even%20need%20a%20cable%20log-in%20for%20ABC%20News%20Live%2C%20which%20you%20can%20access%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FLive%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20will%20be%2090%20minutes%20and%20feature%20two%20commercial%20breaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2263abad12-70ea-4800-b161-01ed1cfd5946%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20are%20the%20moderators%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Muir%2C%20anchor%20of%20ABC's%20flagship%20%26quot%3BWorld%20News%20Tonight%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Linsey%20Davis%2C%20who%20anchors%20the%20Sunday%20edition%20of%20%26quot%3BWorld%20News%20Tonight%26quot%3B%20are%20set%20to%20moderate.%20Both%20journalists%20have%20moderated%20presidential%20primary%20debates%20before%20but%20this%20will%20be%20their%20first%20general%20election%20debate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e4411f2-1ec8-45ce-8a76-381cd4340649%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20the%20mics%20be%20muted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20Harris'%20campaign%20confirmed%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20ABC%20News%20that%20it%20would%20accept%20that%20a%20candidate's%20mic%20will%20be%20muted%20when%20it%20is%20not%20their%20turn%20to%20speak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVice%20President%20Harris%2C%20a%20former%20prosecutor%2C%20will%20be%20fundamentally%20disadvantaged%20by%20this%20format%2C%20which%20will%20serve%20to%20shield%20Donald%20Trump%20from%20direct%20exchanges%20with%20the%20Vice%20President%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Harris%20campaign%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20ABC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20the%20vice%20president's%20campaign%20said%20they%20accepted%20the%20rules%20to%20not%20%26quot%3Bjeopardize%20the%20debate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235466ec5-5c5e-4f9b-8dc5-394bdaa3609b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20else%20will%20this%20be%20different%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-happened-biden-trump-debate-takeaways-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJune's%20Biden-Trump%20debate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20face-off%20fundamentally%20differs%20from%20any%20modern%20major%20presidential%20debate.%20That's%20because%20both%20campaigns%20agreed%20on%20stiff-arming%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-trump-debate-commission-presidential-tradition-over-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Commission%20on%20Presidential%20Debates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20bipartisan%20group%20that%20organized%20presidential%20debates%20for%20decades.%20Republicans%20left%20the%20debate%20commission%20in%202022%2C%20but%20it%20was%20Biden's%20campaign%20that%20delivered%20the%20final%20blow.%20Like%20in%20June%2C%20there%20will%20also%20be%20no%20live%20audience.%20Biden's%20campaign%20said%20in%20May%20that%20muting%20the%20mics%20and%20nixing%20the%20audience%20would%20return%20presidential%20debates%20to%20an%20acceptable%20level%20of%20decorum%20%E2%80%94%20just%20about%20everyone%20agrees%20that%20the%20first%20debate%20in%202020%20was%20an%20abject%20disaster%20as%20Trump%20repeatedly%20interrupted%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222459e33d-bbe8-4891-8cab-a3bd220d5e92%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20questions%20can%20we%20expect%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20Muir%2C%20Davis%2C%20and%20likely%20a%20very%20few%20select%20people%20within%20ABC%20News%20know%20the%20exact%20questions.%20Unlike%20some%20past%20presidential%20debates%2C%20there%20is%20no%20theme%20for%20the%20night.%20That%20all%20being%20said%2C%20it%20is%20a%20virtual%20guarantee%20that%20questions%20related%20to%20the%20economy%20will%20dominate%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolls%20have%20consistently%20shown%20voters%20view%20the%20economy%20as%20the%20biggest%20issue%20in%20the%20election.%20But%20recently%2C%20Harris%20has%20cut%20into%20Trump's%20once%20wide%20advantage%20of%20the%20subject.%20A%20late%20August%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20poll%20found%20that%20Trump%20had%20a%20roughly%20eight-%20percentage%20point%20advantage%20when%20voters%20were%20asked%20who%20would%20best%20handle%20the%20economy.%20He%20also%20held%20a%205-point%20lead%20on%20better%20handling%20inflation.%20His%20margins%20are%20good%2C%20but%20they%20are%20nowhere%20near%20the%2020-point%20advantage%20he%20once%20had%20over%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20both%20issues%20late%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarris%20has%20rolled%20out%20a%20handful%20of%20economic%20plans.%20She%20has%20proposed%20giving%20up%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkamala-harris-economy