d%20to%20myself%20if%20I%20could%20turn%20those%20boring%20weekends%20into%20money-making%20opportunities%20that%20add%20a%20little%20room%20to%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fhow-to-budget%5C%22%3Ebudget%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20was%20yes%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20what%20side%20hustles%20I%20wanted%20to%20say%20yes%20to.%20I%20decided%20to%20hunt%20for%20a%20mix%20of%20potential%20gigs%2C%20and%20ultimately%20found%20four%20side%20hustles%20that%20I%20want%20to%20try%20out.%20I%20calculated%20that%20some%20of%20them%20could%20potentially%20net%20me%20an%20extra%20%241%2C000%20during%20just%20one%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20Renting%20out%20my%20space%20and%20my%20stuff%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20about%20how%20people%20rent%20out%20their%20space%20and%20their%20stuff%20to%20make%20extra%20cash%2C%20I've%20been%20finding%20myself%20eyeing%20my%20apartment%20and%20seeing%20dollar%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20live%20in%20a%20one-bedroom%20apartment%2C%20I%20can%20rent%20it%20out%20to%20people%20who%20are%20looking%20to%20stay%20for%20the%20weekend%20by%20listing%20it%20on%20AirBnB%20for%20%24300%20a%20night%2C%20which%20seems%20to%20be%20the%20going%20rate%20for%20an%20apartment%20my%20size%20and%20in%20my%20location.%20If%20someone%20rents%20it%20out%20for%20four%20nights%2C%20I'd%20earn%20over%20%241%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20other%20options%2C%20too.%20I%20can%20rent%20out%20my%20space%20to%20be%20used%20for%20photoshoots%20or%20small%20events%20on%20Peerspace%20and%20charge%20%24200%20an%20hour%20with%20a%20five-hour%20minimum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20even%20put%20a%20chunk%20of%20my%20space%20on%20Neighbor%2C%20which%20lets%20you%20rent%20out%20your%20space%20for%20people%20to%20use%20as%20storage.%20Depending%20on%20how%20long%20people%20want%20to%20store%20their%20boxes%20or%20items%2C%20I%20think%20I%20can%20earn%20a%20