or%20Bill%20Miller%20IV%20is%20betting%20on%20bitcoin%20to%20achieve%20'digital%20gold'%20status%20within%20the%20next%20decade%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20and%20how%20he%20invests%20in%20the%20cryptocurrency%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bitcoin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fc0536895d82203032dd23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBitcoin%20may%20be%20a%20speculative%20investment%20to%20most%2C%20but%20Bill%20Miller%20IV%20sees%20it%20as%20a%20value%20play.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20predicts%20the%20cryptocurrency%20will%20skyrocket%20in%20value%2C%20and%20thinks%20it%20will%20replace%20fiat%20currencies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMiller%20shares%203%20reasons%20why%20he's%20betting%20on%20bitcoin%20and%20how%20he%20invests%20in%20the%20asset.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EValue%20investing%20and%20bitcoin%20might%20seem%20antithetical%20at%20first%20glance%2C%20but%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvalue-investing-stock-picks-to-buy-tech-nvidia-bill-miller-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBill%20Miller%20IV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20certainly%20isn't%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20investment%20officer%20and%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Miller%20Value%20Partners%20sees%20massive%20untapped%20potential%20in%20bitcoin%20that%20most%20investors%20are%20overlooking.%20Put%20simply%2C%20in%20Miller's%20opinion%2C%20the%20cryptocurrency%20is%20trading%20far%20below%20its%20intrinsic%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20how%20valuable%20is%20bitcoin%20exactly%3F%20%26quot%3BI%20personally%20think%20it's%20the%20new%20denominator%20for%20capital%20globally%20and%20will%20be%20increasingly%20viewed%20as%20a%20standard%20over%20the%20next%20few%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Miller's%20view%2C%20bitcoin%20is%20on%20track%20to%20replace%20fiat%20capital%20and%20completely%20revolutionize%20monetary%20systems%20across%20the%20world.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20compare%20it%20to%20digital%20gold.%20I%20think%20that's%20an%20easy%20eventual%20target%20that%20it%20definitely%20hits%20in%20the%20next%20decade%20or%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b17d548d-dda2-4b7a-99a9-08fd88e9728c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBitcoin%20to%20the%20moon%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20core%20of%20Miller's%20belief%20in%20bitcoin%20is%20its%20finite%20supply.%20The%20same%20can't%20be%20said%20for%20fiat%20currencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bitcoin%20system%20is%20very%2C%20very%20clear%20in%20that%20there's%20only%2021%20million.%20There's%20a%20governed%20supply%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESatoshi%20Nakamoto%2C%20the%20unidentified%20creator%20of%20bitcoin%2C%20developed%20the%20cryptocurrency%20with%20a%20supply%20cap%20to%20prevent%20inflation.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20no%20such%20protocol%20exists%20for%20the%20US%20dollar%20or%20other%20traditional%20currencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happens%20with%20the%20current%20system%20is%20regulators%20and%20politicians%20jockey%20for%20control%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20shift%20the%20ledger%20through%20the%20printing%20of%20more%20dollars%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%20A%20prime%20example%20of%20this%20is%20the%20US%20Treasury%20Department's%20pandemic-era%20printing%20spree%2C%20which%20injected%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20of%20stimulus%20into%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20bitcoin's%20energy-intensive%20mining%20process%20creates%20a%20strong%20value%20proposition%20for%20the%20cryptocurrency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20money%20is%20an%20accountability%20system%2C%20why%20do%20we%20create%20more%20units%20every%20year%3F%26quot%3B%20Miller%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20bitcoin%20has%20a%20%3Cstrong%3Emassive%20total%20addressable%20market%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20a%20compelling%20value%20play%20in%20Miller's%20eyes.%20With%20the%20world's%20fiat%20systems%20approaching%20a%20quadrillion%20dollars%20in%20capital%20and%20bitcoin's%20market%20capitalization%20sitting%20at%20a%20modest%20%241.5%20trillion%2C%20Miller%20sees%20this%20as%20an%20opportunity%20for%20the%20cryptocurrency%20to%20skyrocket%20in%20coming%20years.%20Bitcoin%20is%20massively%20under-owned%20in%20general%20among%20investors%2C%20in%20Miller's%20opinion.%20He%20points%20out%20that%20there%20are%20only%2010.5%20million%20wallets%20with%20over%20%241%2C000%20in%20bitcoin%20holdings%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20individual%20investors%20investing%20in%20bitcoin%2C%20either.%3Cstrong%3E%20Corporations%20are%20increasingly%20investing%20in%20bitcoin%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eby%20adding%20it%20as%20an%20asset%20to%20their%20balance%20sheet%2C%20further%20solidifying%20bitcoin's%20value%20proposition.%20Miller%20highlights%20the%20medical%20technology%20company%20Semler%20Scientific%2C%20which%20has%20been%20reinvesting%20its%20cash%20flow%20into%20the%20cryptocurrency.%20Semler%20Scientific%20currently%20holds%20828%20bitcoins%20in%20total.%20Other%20companies%20such%20as%20Microstrategy%2C%20Metaplanet%2C%20Tesla%2C%20and%20Square%20all%20hold%20bitcoin%20on%20their%20balance%20sheets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20Miller%2C%20bitcoin%20is%20a%20reliable%20form%20of%20currency%20in%20a%20global%20economy%20where%20fiat%20money%20supply%20is%20consistently%20growing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20never%20had%20a%20technology%20before%20that%20enabled%20us%20to%20account%20for%20value%20in%20an%20automated%20way%20or%20in%20automated%20units%20until%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiller's%20arguments%20in%20favor%20of%20bitcoin%20are%20common%20among%20its%20supporters.%20However%2C%20they%20depend%20on%20widespread%20adoption%2C%20and%20it%20remains%20unclear%20how%20realistic%20that%20outcome%20is.%20Many%20other%20cryptocurrencies%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Ethereum%2C%20which%20does%20not%20have%20a%20finite%20supply%20%E2%80%94%20vie%20for%20investors'%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crypto%20space%20also%20faces%20potential%20future%20regulation.%20China%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20banned%20the%20use%20of%20cryptocurrencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f615aa43-908e-4bf2-9bee-e08582d46da6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20invest%20in%20bitcoin%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInvesting%20in%20bitcoin%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20an%20extremely%20risky%20endeavor%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20with%20its%20price%20prone%20to%20frequent%20volatility.%20From%20December%202017%20to%20December%202018%20the%20digital%20currency's%20price%20dropped%2083%25.%20From%20May%202021%20to%20July%202021%20it%20fell%2046%25.%20From%20November%202021%20to%20November%202022%20it%20plunged%2074%25.%20Since%20then%2C%20it%20has%20risen%20236%25%2C%20though%20it's%20down%2019%25%20since%20July%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20their%20volatile%20nature%2C%20many%20financial%20advisors%20recommend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbuying-bitcoin-things-to-consider-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallocating%20only%20a%20very%20small%20part%20of%20one's%20portfolio%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20cryptocurrencies%20like%20bitcoin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20keen%20to%20put%20money%20into%20the%20digital%20asset%2C%20Miller%20believes%20the%20best%20way%20to%20invest%20in%20bitcoin%20is%20just%20to%20buy%20the%20cryptocurrency%20outright.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20recommend%20just%20holding%20it%20directly%2C%20understanding%20the%20mechanics%20of%20self-custody%2C%20so%20that%20you%20are%20the%20only%20one%20that%20controls%20your%20bitcoin%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there's%20been%20a%20rise%20in%20bitcoin%20ETFs%2C%20Miller%20cautions%20against%20gaining%20exposure%20to%20the%20cryptocurrency%20through%20an%20ETF%20vehicle%20and%20recommends%20buying%20it%20directly%20if%20possible.%20To%20Miller%2C%20the%20core%20value%20proposition%20of%20bitcoin%20is%20its%20decentralized%20and%20autonomous%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20own%20it%20in%20a%20centralized%20entity%2C%20you%20force%20someone%20else%20to%20buy%20it%20on%20your%20behalf%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20actually%20hold%20the%20bitcoin%2C%26quot%3B%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20cryptocurrencies%20are%20made%20equally%2C%20either.%20In%20Miller's%20opinion%2C%20many%20other%20cryptocurrencies%20are%20plagued%20by%20the%20same%20governance%20issues%20that%20face%20fiat%20currency%20and%20can't%20replicate%20the%20value%20of%20bitcoin%2C%20which%20is%20why%20bitcoin%20is%20the%20only%20one%20he's%20personally%20invested%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBitcoin%20is%20still%20a%20nascent%20asset%20class%2C%20but%20Miller%20is%20confident%20the%20technology%20has%20a%20clear%20path%20to%20revolutionizing%20the%20global%20monetary%20system%20%E2%80%94%20and%20delivering%20handsome%20returns%20to%20those%20who%20buy%20in%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvalue-investor-bill-miller-betting-bitcoin-skyrocket-digital-gold-cryptocurrency-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725791582000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66da1f905444ffafa762f3cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvalue-investor-bill-miller-betting-bitcoin-skyrocket-digital-gold-cryptocurrency-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bitcoin%20is%20on%20track%20to%20replace%20fiat%20capital%2C%20according%20to%20Bill%20Miller%20IV.%20He%20shares%20why%20bitcoin%20is%20trading%20at%20a%20severe%20discount%20and%20how%20to%20invest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cji%40busin