5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elactose%20intolerant%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20as%20I%20only%20experienced%20the%20unbearable%20pain%20when%20I%20consumed%20dairy%20products.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hopkinsmedicine.org%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-and-diseases%2Flactose-intolerance%23%3A~%3Atext%3DLactose%2520intolerance%2520often%2520runs%2520in%2Cafter%2520a%2520disease%2520or%2520infection.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJohn%20Hopkins%20Medicine%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20says%20that%20symptoms%2C%20which%20include%20bloating%2C%20diarrhea%2C%20stomach%20cramps%2C%20and%20nausea%2C%20may%20start%20during%20the%20teen%20or%20adult%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20I%20loved%20the%20taste%2C%20dairy%20was%20no%20longer%20worth%20consuming.%20Ridding%20it%20from%20my%20diet%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20tall%20task%2C%20especially%20back%20then%2C%20before%20alternatives%20were%20so%20common.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228e190653-2845-4155-a9c1-ad1c0d135b6d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20difficult%20to%20eat%20in%20social%20situations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20found%20that%20restaurants%2C%20especially%20locally-owned%20ones%2C%20don't%20always%20indicate%20on%20the%20menu%20when%20they've%20included%20cream%20or%20cheese%20in%20their%20meals.%20When%20I%20go%20out%20to%20eat%2C%20I%20have%20to%20ask%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-food-allergies-have-eased-but-eating-is-still-complicated-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efood%20preparation%20and%20ingredients%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20That%20annoys%20some%20people%2C%20so%20I%20typically%20stick%20to%20eating%20out%20with%20my%20husband%2C%20close%20family%2C%20and%20friends.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20I%20go%20to%20group%20gatherings%2C%20such%20as%20weddings%2C%20work%20functions%2C%20and%20parties%2C%20I%20will%20likely%20not%20be%20able%20to%20eat%20much%20of%20the%20food%20because%20it%20contains%20dairy.%20I%20usually%20have%20to%20contact%20the%20host%20beforehand%20to%20find%20out%20what's%20on%20the%20menu%20and%20let%20them%20know%20I'll%20need%20a%20dairy-free%20or%20vegan%20option.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20that's%20not%20possible%2C%20I'll%20eat%20whatever%20I%20can%2C%20like%20bread%20or%20a%20side%2C%20and%20then%20go%20out%20to%20eat%20afterward.%20For%20work%20functions%2C%20I%20typically%20don't%20attend%20unless%20they're%20mandatory%2C%20as%20they%20seem%20to%20center%20around%20food%20I%20can't%20consume%3B%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20I%20prefer%20to%20work%20in%20a%20remote%20environment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20also%20more%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-i-wish-i-knew-before-going-dairy-free-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexpensive%20to%20be%20dairy-free%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20When%20I%20go%20out%20for%20coffee%2C%20I%20have%20to%20pay%20extra%20for%20soy%2C%20almond%2C%20or%20oat%20milk.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e4fc805f-affd-4c48-a3a9-6ea68a69c070%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20thankful%20there%20are%20now%20more%20dairy-free%20options%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20home%20is%20my%20safe%20place%2C%20where%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20constantly%20think%20about%20avoiding%20dairy.%20Luckily%2C%20businesses%20such%20as%20ice%20cream%20shops%20and%20grocery%20stores%20have%20become%20way%20more%20inclusive%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20and%20it's%20become%20easier%20to%20find%20non-dairy%20alternatives%20to%20products%20like%20milk%2C%20ice%20cream%2C%20and%20yogurts.%20I%20can%20enjoy%20Ben%20%26amp%3B%20Jerry's%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-dairy-free-ice-creams-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealmond-based%20ice%20cream%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20So%20Delicious's%20coconut%20milk-based%20vanilla%20yogurt%2C%20and%20Silk's%20organic%20soy%20milk%20without%20fear.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResearch%20indicates%20that%20people%20with%20lactose%20intolerance%20and%20those%20who%20have%20issues%20with%20dairy%20can%20handle%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.niddk.nih.gov%2Fhealth-information%2Fdigestive-diseases%2Flactose-intolerance%2Feating-diet-nutrition%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edifferent%20amounts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20lactose.%20That%20has%20been%20confusing%20for%20everyone%20around%20me.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20I've%20learned%20that%20the%20only%20things%20with%20dairy%20that%20I%20can%20handle%20are%20Cheez-Its%2C%20margarine%20(some%20varieties%20of%20margarine%20have%20dairy%2C%20and%20some%20don't)%2C%20and%20baked%20goods%20where%20milk%20is%20cooked%20into%20them%2C%20such%20as%20cookies%2C%20biscuits%2C%20and%20pancakes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20compensate%20for%20my%20lack%20of%20dairy%20intake%2C%20I%20pay%20attention%20to%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Ffoods-high-in-calcium%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecalcium%20intake%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20eat%20foods%20such%20as%20broccoli%2C%20oranges%2C%20collard%20greens%2C%20and%20kale.%20It%20must%20be%20working%20because%20my%20calcium%20levels%20have%20remained%20normal.%20I%20also%20take%20a%20vitamin%20D%20supplement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20grateful%20my%20husband%20is%20so%20accommodating.%20The%20meals%20I%20prepare%20do%20not%20include%20dairy%2C%20but%20if%20my%20husband%20wants%20some%2C%20he'll%20add%20it%20to%20his.%20He%20typically%20orders%20dairy-based%20meals%20when%20we%20eat%20out%20on%20the%20weekends.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20know%20there%20are%20lactase%20tablets%20I%20can%20take%20before%20consuming%20dairy%20products%20to%20help%20with%20digestion.%20I'm%20too%20afraid%20to%20try%20them%2C%20though%2C%20because%20they%20may%20not%20work.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20this%20journey%20has%20been%20challenging%2C%20it%20has%20taught%20me%20to%20be%20more%20inclusive%20and%20mindful%20of%20others'%20dietary%20restrictions%20when%20planning%20gatherings.%20It%20has%20also%20helped%20me%20become%20more%20open%20to%20trying%20new%20foods.%20There%20are%20pros%20and%20cons%20to%20every%20situation.%20You%20just%20have%20to%20find%20the%20positive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feating-dairy-free-diet-social-life-alternatives-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725790682000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d9b5201d8d2deb96b91f51%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feating-dairy-free-diet-social-life-alternatives-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20stopped%20eating%20dairy%2015%20years%20ago.%20The%20diet%20has%20made%20it%20harder%20to%20eat%20with%20friends%2C%20but%20I've%20found%20alternatives%20I%20love%20and%20it's%20made%20me%20feel%20better.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Stephanie%20Claytor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feating-dairy-free-diet-social-life-alternatives-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Spain%20Brings%20Co-Production%20Market%20to%20Toronto%E2%80%99s%20Industry%20Program%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725790619000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2F1-Networking.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3