ake%20Muhlenkamp%20Fund%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Ffunds%2Fmuhlenkamp-fund-us56166y4382%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMUHLX%3C%2Fa%3E)%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D7285dbc291d2df43c1ba944d289f2aaf9c94b311b57e341be58ef1b04e7b8375%26postID%3D66db417b92d5b68ffc4bed2f%26postSlug%3Dinvesting-strategy-top-fund-manager-gold-stocks-ai-artificial-intelligence-2024-9%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.morningstar.com%252Ffunds%252Fxnas%252Fmuhlx%252Fperformance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etopped%2098%25%20of%20the%20funds%20in%20the%20large-cap%20value%20category%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20Morningstar.%20He%20has%20beaten%20his%20benchmark%20in%20each%20of%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20and%20a%20strong%20finish%20to%202024%20could%20extend%20the%20streak%20to%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20fascinating%20is%20that%20Muhlenkamp%20has%20outperformed%20while%20clinging%20tightly%20to%20cash%2C%20even%20though%20conventional%20wisdom%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.investopedia.com%2Fterms%2Fp%2Fperformance_drag.asp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edoing%20so%20can%20weigh%20on%20returns%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20mid-2022%2C%20Muhlenkamp%20said%20he%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-investing-bear-rally-top-fund-manager-strategy-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20staggering%2045%25%20of%20his%20portfolio%20in%20cash%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-stock-picks-to-buy-recession-risk-outlook-inflation-rates-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20cut%20to%2030%25%20in%20early%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20unorthodox%20strategy%20paid%20off%2C%20as%20the%20Muhlenkamp%20Fund%20scored%20a%20positive%20return%20in%202022%2C%20which%20was%20the%20worst%20year%20for%20US%20stocks%20sin