F%2Fwww.investopedia.com%2Fterms%2Ff%2Ffaang-stocks.asp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFAANG%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20acronym%20but%20are%20now%20colloquially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-pay-apple-nvidia-microsoft-alphabet-meta-amazon-tesla-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eknown%20as%20the%20Magnificent%20Seven%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20Big%20Seven.%20Many%20of%20these%20stocks%20have%20been%20rewarded%20for%20going%20all%20in%20on%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20all%20know%20that%20they%20can't%20miss%20the%20next%20big%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Muhlenkamp%20said%20regarding%20AI.%20%26quot%3BThey%20all%20believe%20that%20this%20is%20the%20next%20big%20thing%2C%20and%20they%20all%20have%20very%20deep%20pockets%20to%20go%20spend%20the%20billions%20and%20billions%20and%20billions%20of%20dollars%20that%20are%20required%20to%20deploy%20this%20next%20big%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20AI%20company%20in%20the%20crosshairs%20is%20Nvidia%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnvda-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENVDA%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20which%20had%20been%20the%20market's%20hottest%20stock%20since%20demand%20for%20its%20industry-leading%20chips%20soared%20to%20astronomical%20heights.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-records-biggest-ever-single-day-market-value-loss-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshares%20took%20a%20substantial%20hit%20this%20summer%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20investors%20worried%20that%20AI%20demand%20would%20level%20off%20if%20it%20didn't%20translate%20to%20immediate%20returns%20for%20tech%20giants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20customers%20have%20not%20quite%20yet%20decided%20how%20much%20they're%20willing%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20benefits%20of%20this%20next%20big%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Muhlenkamp%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20all%20the%20tech%20guys%20are%20spending%20their%20capital%2C%20money%20to%20build%20out%20the%20capacity%2C%20and%20I%20think%20it's%20an%20open%20question%20whether%20they%20actually%20get%20a%20good%20return%20on%20their%20investment%20or%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20also%20may%20have%20gone%20overboard%20about%20AI%2C%20Muhlenkamp%20said.%20Nvidia's%20generous%20valuation%20will%20only%20be%20justified%20if%20companies%20keep%20scrambling%20to%20pay%20premiums%20for%20its%20AI%20chips.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20company%20may%20not%20claw%20out%20of%20the%20bear%20market%20it's%20in%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20probably%20more%20like%20Cisco%20in%202000%2C%26quot%3B%20Muhlenkamp%20said%20of%20Nvidia.%20%26quot%3BCisco%20had%20real%20orders.%20I%20mean%2C%20they%20had%20the%20best%20routers%20out%20there%2C%20and%20they%20had%20a%20ridiculous%20backlog%20form%2C%20and%20they%20could%20upcharge%20for%20'em%2C%20and%20were%20building%20out%20the%20internet%20across%20the%20world%2C%20and%20then%20it%20got%20built.%20So%20now%20demand%20drops%20by%20a%20third%20or%20a%20half%2C%20and%20competitors%20come%20online%20with%20cheaper%20products.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20chief%20concern%20for%20Muhlenkamp%20is%20the%20economy.%20He%20estimates%20that%20half%20of%20the%20relevant%20economic%20indicators%20are%20negative%20and%20the%20other%20half%20are%20mixed%2C%20including%20Friday's%20jobs%20report.%20The%20US%20unemployment%20rate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funemployment-rate-job-growth-interest-rate-cuts-federal-reserve-recession-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eticked%20down%20slightly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20while%20employers%20brought%20on%20more%20workers%20in%20August%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funemployment-rate-job-growth-july-labor-market-economic-data-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethan%20in%20July%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20last%20month's%20job%20creation%20number%20still%20undershot%20estimates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20pundits%20have%20all%20but%20ruled%20out%20a%20recession%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-eisman-economy-outlook-financial-crisis-tech-bubble-artificial-intelligence-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%20Steve%20Eisman%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Big%20Short%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20Muhlenkamp%20said%20he%20isn't%20so%20sure.%20The%20odds%20of%20whether%20the%20economy%20contracts%20are%20akin%20to%20a%20coin%20toss%2C%20the%20fund%20manager%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20some%20sectors%20are%20already%20feeling%20the%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Muhlenkamp%20pointed%20out%20that%20US%20stocks%20broadly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fycharts.com%2Findicators%2Fsp_500_pe_ratio%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremain%20richly%20valued%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20economic%20expansion%20could%20continue%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20markets%20should%20be%20accounting%20better%20for%20potential%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20very%2C%20very%20few%20companies%20that%20are%20priced%20as%20if%20the%20market%20expects%20a%20recession%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20manufacturing's%20in%20a%20recession%2C%20trucking%20industry's%20in%20a%20recession%2C%20the%20chip%20industry's%20in%20a%20recession%2C%26quot%3B%20Muhlenkamp%20said.%20%26quot%3BThose%20are%20all%20true%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20reflected%20in%20prices.%20Which%20means%3A%20time%20to%20be%20patient.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282747943-80c4-45f3-8dd5-d62c831f2dbe%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20golden%20opportunity%20for%20investors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20a%20market%20where%20discounts%20are%20scarce%2C%20Muhlenkamp%20has%20investments%20where%20he'd%20put%20money%20to%20work%2C%20including%20companies%20connected%20to%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGold%20started%20hitting%20these%20all-time%20highs%2C%20and%20none%20of%20the%20gold-related%20stocks%20were%20moving%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Muhlenkamp%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20said%2C%20'Wow%2C%20what%20an%20opportunity.'%20The%20opportunity%20is%20still%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20yellow%20metal%20has%20snapped%20out%20of%20a%20yearslong%20malaise%20by%20rising%2022%25%20this%20year%2C%20though%20Muhlenkamp%20noted%20that%20gold%20mining%20stocks%20like%20%3Cstrong%3ENewmont%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fnem-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENEM%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20%3Cstrong%3ERoyal%20Gold%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Frgld-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERGLD%3C%2Fa%3E)%20didn't%20catch%20fire%20until%20late%20March.%20Those%20companies%2C%20which%20are%20now%20two%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmuhlenkamp.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMuhlenkamp's%20larger%20holdings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20up%2049%25%20and%2022%25%20since%20then%2C%20respectively%2C%20but%20he%20believes%20they're%20still%20undervalued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Newmont%20is%20trading%20more%20than%2040%25%20below%20its%20all-time%20high%20from%20April%202022%2C%20even%20though%20gold%20is%20near%20a%20record%20of%20its%20own.%20Muhlenkamp%20doesn't%20see%20a%20reason%20for%20the%20disconnect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20thinking%20is%20always%3A%20cheap%2C%20hated%2C%20and%20in%20an%20uptrend%2C%26quot%3B%20Muhlenkamp%20said%20of%20his%20strategy.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20you%20start%20looking%20at%20cheap%20and%20hated%2C%20that's%20usually%20a%20good%20place%20to%20start%20looking%20for%20good%20prices%20on%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGold%20isn't%20just%20a%20stronghold%20against%20a%20weaker%20economy%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20also%20a%20time-tested%20hedge%20against%20higher%20inflation.%20Muhlenkamp%20fears%20that%20inflation%20could%20reaccelerate%20to%203%25%20or%204%25%20going%20forward%20since%20government%20spending%20is%20much%20higher%20than%20what%20he's%20comfortable%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20devaluing%20the%20currency%20against%20real%20things%20%E2%80%94%20real%2C%20tangible%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Muhlenkamp%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20that's%20crude%20oil%2C%20whether%20that's%20gold%2C%20whether%20that's%20a%20house%2C%20it%20takes%20more%20greenbacks%20to%20go%20buy%20the%20same%20darn%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-eisman-economy-outlook-financial-crisis-tech-bubble-artificial-intelligence-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUnlike%20Eisman%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Muhlenkamp%20has%20serious%20doubts%20about%20the%20US%20dollar%2C%20which%20is%20why%20he%20said%20his%20allocation%20to%20gold-related%20investments%20is%207%25%20to%208%25%20%E2%80%94%20the%20highest%20it's%20ever%20been.%20Based%20on%20his%20enviable%20track%20record%2C%20investors%20may%20want%20to%20follow%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20getting%20a%20lot%20more%20traction%20in%20terms%20of%20actually%20using%20gold%20as%20a%20currency%2C%20things%20that%20we%20haven't%20seen%20in%2C%20what%2C%2070%20years%3F%26quot%3B%20Muhlenkamp%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20predicting%20that%20that%20continues%20to%20happen%2C%20but%20if%20it%20does%20continue%20to%20happen%2C%20then%20I%20think%20the%20price%20of%20gold%20will%20move%20up%20very%20nicely.%20And%20that%20gives%20a%20nice%20risk-reward%20there%20for%20companies%20that%20have%20exposure%20to%20the%20price%20of%20gold.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221606%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gold%20in%20bull%20steepening%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66db57eea0ff598b266584b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221076%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERIA%20Advisors%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMuhlenkamp%20isn't%20alone%20with%20this%20call.%20Michael%20Lebowitz%20of%