20your%20needs%20%E2%80%94%20all%20your%20needs%20%E2%80%94%20while%20you%20get%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20running%20away%20from%20a%20track%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c4fd9b1aa2ac29ee32ae6f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221342%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt's%20not%20that%20the%20women%20hate%20their%20jobs%2C%20or%20don't%20care%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20work%20they%20do.%20It's%20that%20their%20previous%20dreams%20of%20climbing%20the%20corporate%20ladder%20now%20strike%20them%20as%20laughably%20tiny.%3Cp%3EKiersten%20Essenpreis%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20many%20of%20the%20other%20women%20have%20settled%20on%20their%20own%2010x%20goals.%20A%20nonprofit%20CEO%20announces%20she%20wants%20to%20run%20for%20governor%20of%20her%20state.%20A%20deputy%20CEO%20who%20has%20a%20side%20hustle%20as%20a%20solopreneur%20wants%20to%20get%20her%20product%20on%20%26quot%3BShark%20Tank.%26quot%3B%20A%20wealth%20advisor%20who%20runs%20her%20own%20firm%20wants%20to%20host%20a%20TV%20show%20on%20issues%20facing%20women.%20The%20consultant%20who%20called%20herself%20a%20follower%20decides%20she%20does%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20want%20to%20be%20the%20top%20boss%20of%20the%20company%20she%20intends%20to%20start.%20The%20communications%20manager%20who%20cried%20on%20the%20first%20day%20about%20wanting%20to%2010x%20her%20confidence%20says%20she%20wants%20to%20focus%20instead%20on%20what%20she's%20good%20at%20%E2%80%94%20being%20joyful%20%E2%80%94%20and%20instill%20that%20in%20her%20four%20kids.%20A%20neurologist%20vows%20to%20live%20a%20more%20interconnected%20life%20with%20nature.%20Two%20other%20consultants%20want%20to%20find%20a%20partner.%20The%20HR%20executive%20wants%20to%20change%20someone's%20life%2C%20though%20she's%20not%20sure%20what%20form%20that%20will%20take.%20The%20auditor%20who%20yesterday%20wasn't%20sure%20she%20wanted%20kids%20decides%20that%20she%20does%20%E2%80%94%20a%20conversation%20she'll%20need%20to%20have%20with%20her%20boyfriend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20women%20are%20surprised%20by%20their%20goals.%20If%20you%20asked%20them%20to%20state%20their%20ambitions%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20they%20would%20have%20been%20entirely%20focused%20on%20advancing%20their%20careers.%20They%20wanted%20to%20make%20partner%20at%20their%20firm%2C%20join%20the%20C-suite%2C%20expand%20their%20business%2C%20double%20their%20salary%2C%20get%20the%20corner%20office.%20The%20fact%20that%20their%20new%20goals%20have%20almost%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20big%2C%20prestigious%2C%20high-paying%20jobs%20that%20have%20brought%20them%20such%20extraordinary%20success%20isn't%20just%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20power%20of%20Byars'%20program.%20It%20also%20says%20something%20about%20the%20moment%20we're%20in%20today%2C%20after%20a%20yearslong%20national%20reckoning%20with%20the%20role%20of%20work%20in%20our%20lives.%20It's%20not%20that%20these%20women%20hate%20their%20current%20jobs%2C%20or%20that%20they%20don't%20care%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20work%20they%20do.%20It's%20that%20their%20previous%20dreams%20of%20climbing%20the%20corporate%20ladder%20now%20strike%20them%20as%20laughably%20%3Cem%3Etiny%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20pandemic%20killed%20hustle%20culture%2C%20some%20commentators%20dubbed%20it%20%26quot%3Bthe%20age%20of%20anti-ambition.%26quot%3B%20But%20in%20this%20hyper-elite%20crowd%20of%2050%20women%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20me%20the%20exact%20opposite.%20Their%20ambitions%20today%2C%20no%20longer%20constrained%20by%20the%20limitations%20of%20the%20corporate%20workplace%2C%20are%20way%20bigger%20than%20they%20ever%20could%20have%20imagined.%20And%20even%20though%20I%20spent%20the%20weekend%20questioning%20the%20wisdom%20of%20aiming%20ever%20higher%2C%20I%20wonder%20if%20the%20women%20are%2C%20by%20the%20very%20act%20of%20set