ontent%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20development%20in%20strife-torn%20Manipur%2C%20the%20N%20Biren%20Singh-led%20BJP%20government%20has%20demanded%20control%20of%20the%20Unified%20Command%20that%20oversees%20security%20operations%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20state%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20The%20Command%20is%20currently%20handled%20by%20a%20team%20of%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20officials%2C%20the%20state%20security%20adviser%20and%20the%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20said%20that%20Chief%20Minister%20Singh%20and%20all%20MLAs%20of%20the%20state%20have%20submitted%20a%20list%20of%20demands%20to%20Governor%20Lakshman%20Acharya.%20On%20this%20list%20is%20a%20demand%20for%20%26quot%3Badequate%20powers%20and%20responsibilities%20to%20the%20elected%20State%20government%20as%20per%20the%20Constitution%20by%20handing%20over%20Unified%20Command%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20source%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20demand%20in%20the%20list%20is%20the%20scrapping%20of%20a%20Suspension%20of%20Operations%20agreement%20between%20the%20government%20and%20Kuki%20insurgent%20groups%20to%20enable%20security%20forces%20to%20crack%20down%20hard.%20In%20January%20this%20year%2C%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20in%20Manipur%20had%20asked%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20government%20to%20scrap%20the%20agreement%20so%20that%20security%20forces%20can%20launch%20full-scale%20operations%20against%20Kuki%20insurgents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20meeting%2C%20chaired%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Singh%2C%20Opposition%20MLAs%20had%20also%20questioned%20why%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20state%20government%20had%20not%20informed%20that%20Article%20355%20of%20the%20Constitution%20was%20in%20force%20in%20Manipur.%20Article%20355%20states%20that%20it%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20Union%20to%20protect%20every%20state%20against%20external%20aggression%20and%20internal%20disturbance%20and%20imposition%20of%20this%20provision%20means%20that%20state%20is%20one%20step%20away%20from%20President's%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20also%20calls%20upon%20the%20Centre%20to%20ensure%20peace%20in%20the%20state%20that%20is%20suffering%20due%20to%20a%20cycle%20of%20violence%20following%20ethnic%20classes%20in%20May%20last%20year.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20MLAs%20have%20also%20demanded%20protection%20of%20the%20state's%20territorial%20integrity%2C%20completion%20of%20border%20fencing%2C%20a%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20exercise%20and%20the%20deportation%20of%20all%20illegal%20migrants%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meitei%20community%20and%20the%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20tribes%20known%20as%20Kukis%2C%20who%20are%20dominant%20in%20some%20hill%20areas%20of%20Manipur%2C%20has%20killed%20over%20220%20people%20and%20internally%20displaced%20nearly%2050%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20category%20Meiteis%20want%20to%20be%20included%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20category%2C%20while%20the%20Kukis%20who%20share%20ethnic%20ties%20with%20people%20in%20neighbouring%20Myanmar's%20Chin%20State%20and%20Mizoram%20want%20a%20separate%20administration%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur%2C%20citing%20discrimination%20and%20unequal%20share%20of%20resources%20and%20power%20with%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725788460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F94t2u7g8_biren-singh_625x300_30_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-chief-minister-seeks-unified-command-control-to-end-violence-6517451%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20significant%20development%20in%20strife-torn%20Manipur%2C%20the%20N%20Biren%20Singh-led%20BJP%20government%20has%20demanded%20control%20of%20the%20Unified%20Command%20that%20oversees%20security%20operations%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20state%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22