t%20Fulfill%20Prayers%20Are%20Put%20On%20Trial%2C%20Punished%20In%20This%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChhattisgarh's%20tribal-dominated%20Bastar%20region%20has%20often%20made%20headlines%20for%20kangaroo%20courts%20in%20which%20Maoists%20mete%20out%20punishments.%20But%20Bastar%20has%20another%20court%20that%20meets%20once%20a%20year%20and%20even%20Gods%20are%20not%20immune%20to%20its%20sentences.%20This%20court%2C%20which%20meets%20at%20a%20temple%2C%20holds%20Gods%20guilty%20and%20also%20punishes%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bastar%20region%2C%20where%20tribals%20account%20for%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20population%2C%20is%20seeped%20in%20myth%20and%20folklore.%20The%20tribes%20--%20Gond%2C%20Maria%2C%20Bhatra%2C%20Halba%20and%20Dhurwa%20--%20practice%20many%20traditions%20that%20are%20unheard%20of%20outside%20the%20region%20and%20form%20a%20key%20part%20of%20Bastar's%20rich%20heritage.%20One%20of%20them%20is%20the%20jan%20adalat%20--%20meaning%20people's%20court%20--%20that%20meets%20at%20Bhangaram%20Devi%20temple%20during%20Bhado%20Jatra%20festival%20every%20year%20during%20the%20monsoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F05n1bq08_bastar-temple_625x300_08_September_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrial%20And%20Punishment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20three-day%20festival%2C%20the%20temple's%20deity%20Bhangaram%20Devi%20presides%20over%20trials%20in%20which%20Gods%20are%20accused%20and%20animals%20and%20birds%20--%20often%20hens%20-%20are%20witnesses.%20The%20villagers%20are%20the%20complainants%20--%20complaints%20range%20from%20a%20failed%20harvest%20to%20a%20lingering%20illness%20and%20can%20include%20anything%20for%20which%20prayers%20were%20not%20answered.%20The%20punishments%20are%20harsh.%20A%20God%20found%20guilty%20is%20sentenced%20to%20exile%20--%20their%20idols%2C%20mostly%20wooden%20totems%2C%20lose%20their%20place%20inside%20the%20temple%20and%20are%20banished%20to%20its%20backyard.%20Sometimes%2C%20this%20punishment%20is%20for%20life%20or%20till%20they%20mend%20their%20ways%20and%20get%20their%20seat%20in%20the%20temple%20back.%20People%20from%20around%20240%20villages%20gather%20to%20see%20the%20gods%20on%20trial.%20A%20feast%20is%20arranged%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20festival%2C%20which%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20India's%20rich%20diversity%2C%20is%20an%20idea%20that%20even%20Gods%20are%20accountable%20to%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fjqnjbgoo_bastar-temple_625x300_08_September_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Chance%20Of%20Redemption%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrials%20at%20Bhangaram%20Devi%20Temple%20are%20not%20just%20about%20punishment%2C%20but%20reformation%20too.%20Gods%20are%20given%20an%20opportunity%20to%20redeem%20themselves.%20If%20they%20rectify%20their%20behaviour%20and%20answer%20the%20people's%20prayers%2C%20they%20get%20their%20temple%20seat%20back.%20If%20not%2C%20the%20exile%20continues.%20Historian%20Ghanshyam%20Singh%20Nag%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20tradition%20represents%20the%20idea%20that%20the%20relationship%20between%20gods%20and%20humans%20is%20reciprocal.%20Gods%20protect%20and%20provide%20for%20the%20people%2C%20and%20in%20return%2C%20they%20are%20worshipped.%20If%20this%20balance%20is%20disturbed%2C%20even%20gods%20are%20judged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20approach%20the%20divine%20court%20if%20they%20believe%20their%20Gods%20failed%20them%20during%20times%20of%20need%20--%20this%20may%20include%20disease%20outbreaks%2C%20natural%20calamities%20or%20a%20bad%20harvest.%20Then%20the%20Gods%20are%20summoned%20and%20punished%20after%20trial.%20If%20the%20Gods%20mend%20their%20ways%20--%20the%20village%20gets%20rain%20or%20good%20fortune%20--%20they%20are%20welcomed%20back%20from%20exile.%C2%A0Farsu%20Salam%2C%20a%20member%20of%20Bhangaram%20Temple%20Committee%2C%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20villagers%20believe%20that%20the%20Gods%20responsible%20for%20solving%20their%20problems%20have%20failed%2C%20they%20are%20brought%20here%20for%20trial.%20This%20happens%20once%20a%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fmqu0vpl8_bastar-temple_625x300_08_September_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELawyers%20And%20Witnesses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVillage%20leaders%20serve%20as%20lawyers%20in%20this%20divine%20court%20and%20hens%20are%20witnesses.%20A%20hen%20is%20brought%20to%20the%20court%20and%20set%20free%20after%20the%20trial%2C%20marking%20the%20end%20of%20its%20testimony.%20The%20sentence%20is%20pronounced%20by%20a%20village%20leader%2C%20believed%20to%20be%20voicing%20the%20goddess's%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20punished%20gods%20are%20then%20removed%20from%20the%20temple%20and%20sometimes%20placed%20under%20trees%20--%20a%20symbolic%20imprisonment.%20The%20gold%20or%20silver%20decorations%20on%20the%20idols%20are%20not%20removed.%20There%20have%20been%20no%20reports%20of%20theft%20as%20the%20tribals%20believe%20such%20an%20act%20will%20invite%20divine%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20any%20court%2C%20a%20ledger%20is%20maintained%20that%20lists%20details%20of%20every%20case%20-%20the%20number%20of%20deities%20accused%2C%20the%20nature%20of%20their%20alleged%20crimes%2C%20the%20witnesses%2C%20and%20the%20final%20judgments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20maintain%20a%20register%20where%20we%20document%20everything%2C%20from%20how%20many%20gods%20appeared%20to%20how%20many%20were%20punished%2C%26quot%3B%20Farsu%20Salam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F4tun97f_bastar-temple_625x300_08_September_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAppeals%20Against%20Sentences%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20regular%20legal%20system%2C%20a%20sentence%20can%20be%20appealed%20in%20a%20higher%20court.%20But%20at%20Bastar's%20divine%20court%2C%20the%20appeals%20must%20be%20filed%20before%20Bhangaram%20Devi%2C%20who%20pronounced%20the%20sentence.%20If%20the%20exiled%20Gods%20seek%20forgiveness%20and%20convince%20the%20deity%2C%20their%20exile%20sentence%20is%20suspended%20and%20they%20can%20return%20to%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoetess%20Poonam%20Vasam%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20social%20system.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20just%20as%20humans%20are%20responsible%20for%20fulfilling%20their%20duties%20in%20the%20society%2C%20the%20gods%20too%20must%20bear%20responsibility.%20If%20they%20fail%20to%20protect%20or%20help%20their%20people%2C%20they%20too%20face%20punishment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fddrg7nvg_bastar-temple_625x300_08_September_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Temple%20And%20The%20Deity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tribes%20in%20Bastar%20have%20their%20gods%20and%20goddesses.%20According%20to%20the%20local%20folklore%2C%20many%20of%20them%20were%20humans%20earlier%20and%20were%20elevated%20to%20the%20divine%20status%20for%20their%20noble%20deeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhangaram%20Devi%2C%20local%20residents%20believe%2C%20came%20to%20Bastar%20centuries%20ago%20from%20Warangal%20in%20present-day%20Telangana.%20Along%20with%20her%20came%20%26quot%3BDr%20Khan%26quot%3B%20from%20Nagpur.%20The%20temple%2C%20according%20to%20local%20residents%2C%20was%20built%20in%20during%20the%20reign%20of%20King%20Bhairamdev%20in%20the%2019th%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20village%20Sarju%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Mai%20ji%20came%20from%20Warangal%2C%20she%20asked%20the%20local%20king%20for%20a%20place%20to%20settle.%20She%20was%20given%20land%20near%20the%20mountains%20of%20Keshkal.%20Along%20with%20her%20came%20Dr%20Khan%2C%20who%20served%20the%20tribals%20during%20cholera%20and%20smallpox%20outbreaks.%26quot%3B%20Over%20time%2C%20Dr%20Khan%20has%20acquired%20divine%20status%20and%20is%20known%20as%20Khan%20Devta%20or%20%26quot%3BKaana%20Doctor%26quot%3B.%20Villagers%20now%20offer%20lemons%20and%20eggs%20to%20the%20deity.%20'Khan%20Devta'%20resides%20along%20with%20other%20deities%20at%20Bhangaram%20Devi%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725785160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F5v5pkgu8_bangaram-devi_625x300_08_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbastar-chhattisgarh-gods-are-put-on-trial-punished-in-this-divine-court-in-chhattisgarh-6517393%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chhattisgarh's%20tribal-dominated%20Bastar%20region%20has%20often%20made%20headlines%20for%20kangaroo%20courts%20in%20which%20Maoists%20mete%20out%20punishments.%20But%20Bastar%20has%20another%20court%20that%20meets%20once%20a%20year%20and%20even%20Gods%20are%20not%20immune%20to%20its%20sentences%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Ends%20Paris%20Paralympics%20With%2029%20Medals.%20Pakistan%2C%20China%20Got...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Paris%20Paralympic%20Games%202024%20concluded%20for%20India%20on%20Sunday%2C%20with%20Pooja%20Ojha%20the%20final%20athlete%20in%20action.%20Ojha%20failed%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20women's%20kayak%20200m%20final%20and%20bowed%20out%20of%20the%20competition.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20India's%20medals%20tally%20at%20the%20Paris%20Paralympics%20ended%20at%2029%20--%20seven%20golds%2C%20nine%20silvers%20and%2013%20bronze%2C%20making%20it%20the%20most%20rewarded%20campaign%20for%20the%20country.%20Courtesy%20of%20the%2029%20medals%2C%20India%20stood%20at%20the%2018th%20position%20in%20the%20points%20table.%20Pakistan%2C%20who%20were%20also%20competing%20win%20the%20event%2C%20ended%20the%20campaign%20joint-bottom%20at%20the%2079th%20position%2C%20with%20just%20a%20solitary%20bronze%20to%20its%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20did%20very%20well%20in%20the%202024%20campaign%2C%20beating%20top%20nations%20like%20Switzerland%2C%20Belgium%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Turkey%2C%20Argentina%2C%20etc.%20to%20finish%20the%20Paris%20Para%20Games%20among%20the%20top%2020%20countries%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fp1vs3vgg_medal-tally_625x300_08_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%20to%20India%2C%20the%20traditional%20heavyweights%20at%20the%20Paralympic%20Games%20--%20China%2C%20Great%20Britain%2C%20USA%2C%20Italy%2C%20etc.%20did%20very%20well%20gain%2C%20finishing%20among%