released%20a%20statement%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BQueen%20Elizabeth%20the%20Queen%20Mother%20has%20bequeathed%20her%20entire%20estate%20(which%20mainly%20comprises%20the%20contents%20of%20her%20houses)%20to%20the%20Queen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20her%20will%2C%20she%20requested%20that%20the%20Queen%20make%20certain%20bequests%20to%20members%20of%20her%20staff%2C%20and%20these%20bequests%20will%20be%20subject%20to%20inheritance%20tax%20as%20usual.%20The%20Queen%20has%20decided%20that%20the%20most%20important%20of%20Queen%20Elizabeth's%20pictures%20and%20works%20of%20art%20should%20be%20transferred%20to%20the%20Royal%20Collection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725778380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fr62pavj_prince-harry_625x300_21_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprince-harry-to-inherit-17-million-on-40th-birthday-from-queen-mother-6516928%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Duke%20of%20Sussex%20will%20be%20eligible%20to%20receive%20a%20substantial%20sum%20on%20September%2015%20from%20a%20trust%20established%20by%20Queen%20Elizabeth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprince-harry-to-inherit-17-million-on-40th-birthday-from-queen-mother-6516928%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Signature%20Global%20gives%20Rs%201%2C144%20cr%20order%20for%20housing%20project%20in%20Gurugram%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725778095000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-09%2F04%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1725461099-5157.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsignature-global-gives-rs-1-144-cr-order-for-housing-project-in-gurugram-124090800146_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Realty%20firm%20Signature%20Global%20has%20give