%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Lin%20told%20the%20outlet.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20foreign%20body%20was%20wrapped%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20phlegm.%20After%20removing%20the%20surrounding%20phlegm%2C%20we%20discovered%20it%20was%20a%20cockroach.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bug%20was%20carefully%20removed%20from%20the%20man's%20trachea%2C%20and%20the%20area%20was%20cleaned%20thoroughly.%20The%20foul%20odour%20the%20patient%20had%20experienced%20disappeared%20soon%20after.%20He%20made%20a%20full%20recovery%20and%20was%20discharged%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Dr%20Lin%20noted%20that%20such%20unusual%20cases%20are%20rare%2C%20he%20advised%20anyone%20who%20suspects%20they%20have%20a%20foreign%20body%20lodged%20in%20their%20lower%20respiratory%20tract%20to%20seek%20medical%20attention%20immediately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725776400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fp9qbbtg_cockroaches_625x300_14_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fman-wakes-up-to-find-cockroach-stuck-in-throat-heres-what-happened-next-6516721%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2058-year-old%20Chinese%20man%20experienced%20an%20entomophobe's%20worst%20nightmare%20after%20discovering%20a%20cockroach%20had%20lodged%20itself%20in%20his%20trachea.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fman-wakes-up-to-find-cockroach-stuck-in-throat-heres-what-happened-next-6516721%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kangana%20's%20Emergency%20puts%20spotlight%20on%20Bollywood%20and%20Censors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725776074000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113162371%2Cimgsize-84746.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkangana-ranauts-emergency-brings-the-spotlight-on-bollywoods-dispute-wit