0and%20Goa%20within%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCfA9pX3DaB2%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCfA9pX3DaB2%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCfA9pX3DaB2%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Silaiwali%20(%40silaiwali)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20handcrafted%20items%20by%20SilaiWali%20range%20from%20Rs%20820%20to%20Rs%205400.%20The%20brand%20exports%20goods%20worth%20%24200%2C000%20every%20year%2C%20with%20peak%20seasons%20around%20September%20to%20December%20to%20cater%20to%20Christmas%20and%20Halloween%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20SilaiWali%20claims%20to%20have%20trained%20and%20reskilled%20325%20women%20refugees.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20one%20point%2C%20we%20had%20150%20such%20women%20working%20with%20us.%20But%20most%20of%20them%20migrated%20to%20Canada%20due%20to%20changing%20immigration%20policies%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Bishwadeep.%20Despite%20facing%20such%20challenges%2C%20SilaiWali%20continues%20to%20make%20a%20significant%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20wages%20of%20the%20artisans%2C%20Bishwadeep%20says%20it%20is%20calculated%20following%20the%20wage%20ladder%20mandated%20by%20the%20World%20Fair%20Trade%20Organisation.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20incomes%20vary%20from%20artisan%20to%20artisan%2C%20they%20earn%20between%20Rs%2012%2C000%20to%20Rs%2014%2C000%20every%20month.%20It%20can%20also%20increase%20depending%20on%20factors%20like%20sales%20and%20special%20orders%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20her%20experience%20of%20working%20with%20these%20women%2C%20Iris%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfghan%20women%20have%20a%20pleasant%20demeanour.%20They%20are%20very%20proud%20of%20their%20heritage.%20They%20listen%20to%20my%20instructions%20and%20are%20not%20afraid%20to%20disagree%20with%20me%20when%20necessary.%20They%20have%20shown%20amazing%20resilience%20in%20rebuilding%20their%20lives%20in%20India%2C%20however%20temporary%20their%20current%20residence%20may%20be.%20Many%20SilaiWali%20women%20have%20broken%20the%20glass%20ceiling%20by%20being%20the%20sole-earning%20members%20of%20their%20families.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20these%20families%20were%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20Their%20children%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20sent%20to%20school.%20We%20are%20glad%20that%20our%20intervention%20has%20somewhat%20eased%20their%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Iris%2C%20who%20finds%20this%20work%20extremely%20fulfilling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20his%20decision%20to%20quit%20journalism%20to%20establish%20a%20career%20in%20the%20social%20enterprise%20sector%2C%20Bishwadeep%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20do%20impacts%20so%20many%20families%20and%20provides%20them%20with%20dignity%2C%20spending%20power%2C%20demolishing%20the%20patriarchal%20system%2C%20and%20creating%20an%20impact%20that%20can%20be%20seen%20on%20the%20ground.%20This%20work%20gave%20me%20an%20opportunity%20to%20directly%20engage%20with%20the%20marginalised%20sections%20at%20the%20grassroots.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20SilaiWali%20social%20verticals.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725030423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSilaiWali-1-1725019598.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D363502%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iris%20Strill%20and%20Bishwadeep%20Moitra%20founded%20SilaiWali%2C%20a%20social%20enterprise%20in%20India%20that%20empowers%20Afghan%20refugee%20women%20by%20helping%20them%20turn%20waste%20fabric%20into%20handcrafted%20rag%20dolls.%20Through%20this%2C%20they%20have%20also%20diverted%20around%2015%2C000%20kg%20of%20fabric%20from%20landfills%20so%20far.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F363502%2Firis-strill-bishwadeep-moitra-silaiwali-upcycled-ragdolls-empower-afghan-women-refugees-financial-freedom%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20This%20Startup%E2%80%99s%20Innovation%20Can%20Save%20Over%203000%20Kg%20Of%20Paper%20Waste%20From%20Reaching%20Landfills%20Every%20Month%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20was%20a%20tough%20time%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20including%20businesses.%20The%20situation%20was%20bleak%20at%20Chikkamagaluru%20too%2C%20at%20BG%20Boutique%20Paper%20Mills%20Private%20Limited.%20BG%20Seetharaman%2C%20Founder%20and%20Managing%20Director%20of%20the%20company%2C%20faced%20a%20tough%20time%20in%20keeping%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348979%2Fcotton-waste-from-factories-sustainable-stationery-rashi-agarwal-roohani-rang-recycled-diary-notebooks-support-artisans%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehandmade%20paper%20company%20%3C%2Fa%3Erunning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPassionate%20about%20sustainability%20and%20preventing%20agricultural%20and%20plastic%20waste%20from%20entering%20the%20landfills%2C%20he%20used%20the%20time%20to%20brainstorm%20ideas%20to%20work%20on%20his%20dream%20project%20which%20was%20an-end-to-end%20solution%20that%20would%20prevent%20solid%20wastes%20from%20entering%20landfills.%20But%20how%20could%20that%20be%20done%3F%20By%20developing%20a%20machine%20that%20recycles%20waste%20at%20source.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20discussed%20this%20idea%20with%20Vinay%20Kumar%2C%20a%20social%20entrepreneur%2C%20and%20Rajeeva%20Deekshit%2C%20a%20green%20chemical%20expert%2C%20over%20the%20next%20few%20months.%20They%20came%20to%20a%20conclusion%20that%20the%20two%20areas%20they%20wanted%20to%20target%20were%20waste%20paper%20and%20fibrous%20agricultural%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founders%20is%20that%2C%20about%2030%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20paper%20is%20getting%20into%20the%20landfills%20due%20to%20being%20coated%20with%20plastic%20or%20aluminium%20and%20are%20contaminated%20with%20beverages%20that%20makes%20it%20unsuitable%20for%20recycling.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20almost%2087%20million%20tonnes%20of%20crop%20residue%20is%20burned%20annually%20in%20India%2C%20as%20per%20a%20Science%20Direct%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-58-1725024679.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22B%20G%20Seetharaman%2C%20Vinay%20Kumar%20and%20Rajeeva%20Deekshit%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-58-1725024679.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebe